org.anchoranalysis.plugin.io.bean.descriptivename

Class RemoveExtensions

  • Object
    • AnchorBean<FileNamer>
      • FileNamer
        • RemoveExtensions

  • public class RemoveExtensions
extends FileNamer
    Removes extensions from the descriptive-name (but not from the file) AND only if the extension hasn't already been removed upstream.

    As an exception, the extension can be retained if there is more than one file with the same descriptive-name

    To check if the extension has already been removed upstream, a check occurs if the path ends with the descriptive-name

    Author:
    Owen Feehan
